HEADWORD: Metol
<hw>Me"tol</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G.; trade name, fr.
<ets>meta-</ets> + kre<ets>sol</ets> cresol.]</ety> <def>A whitish
soluble powder used as a developer in photography. Chemically, it is the
